</b></p>
<p><b>the economic, social and cultural rights, including a rise in the minimum wage 
</b></p>
<p><b>(Indonesia); 
</b></p>
<p>140.51.<b>  Protect the rights of the vulnerable groups of the population, such as 
women, children, persons with disabilities and elderly persons (Afghanistan); 
</b></p>
<p>140.52.<b> Continue efforts to promote the rights of the vulnerable and 
marginalized groups in the country (Nepal); 
</b></p>
