<p>140.106.<b> Further enhance the prevention of domestic violence (Myanmar); 
</b></p>
<p>140.107.<b> Fast track the drafting of a federal bill on prevention of violence in 
the family (South Africa); 
</b></p>
<p>140.108.<b> Continue its efforts to enact laws addressing domestic violence, 
