</b></p>
<p><b>on the Rights of Indigenous Peoples (Estonia); 
</b></p>
<p>140.225.<b> Increase its budget allocation for indigenous peoples (Namibia); 
</b></p>
<p>140.226.<b> Standardize the legal requirements for migrant workers, taking into 
