of their families, by ratifying in particular the related international convention 
</b></p>
<p><b>(Burkina Faso); 
</b></p>
<p>140.229.<b> Take action to stop the atrocities committed by some individuals 
against immigrants, especially in Moscow (Chad); 
</b></p>
<p>140.230.<b> Step up efforts in the field of international development assistance 
(Bangladesh); 
</b></p>
<p>140.231.<b> Strengthen its measure to protect its citizens from terrorism and 
