</b></p>
<p>141.<b> In the view of the Russian Federation, the recommendations in the footnote 
below are not relevant as they do not comply with the basis of the review stipulated in 
</b></p>
<p><b>Human Rights Council Resolutions nos. 5/1 and 16/21.</b>1<b> 
</b></p>
<p>142.<b> All conclusions and/or recommendations contained in the present report reflect 
the position of the submitting State(s) and/or the State under review. They should not 
</b></p>
<p><b>be construed as endorsed by the Working Group as a whole.</b> 
